### Create a performance review
POST http://{{host}}:{{port}}/employees/1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reviewerId": 2,
  "reviewDate": "2025-01-15T10:00:00Z",
  "performanceScore": 8,
  "softSkillsScore": 9,
  "independenceScore": 7,
  "aspirationForGrowthScore": 8,
  "notes": "Excellent work this quarter."
}

### Optional environment defaults for IntelliJ HTTP Client
### @name env
@host=localhost
@port=8080
